nodes.text: Che'nash was a female Geranite mercenary operative working as part of the Shrikaansi Reconnaissance Company for the reconstituted Sith Empire at the end of the Cold War.

Che'nash was a part of a mercenary team, hired by the Sith Empire and deployed to the planet Ilum at the end of the Cold War. Her team was tasked with uncovering information on a Republic operation code named "Shatterstorm", which involved the Republic's Talz commandos. However, they were unable to complete their mission alone, and were forced to seek the help of other Imperial operatives.
Che'nash first appeared in the MMORPG Star Wars: The Old Republic, released by BioWare in 2011.
She is only accessible to Imperial players in the game on Ilum.
